comments: Tatum (BOS) briefly places his hand to Harden's (HOU) front/arm as he moves along his path during the drive.
Brown (BOS) makes marginal contact with Westbrook's (HOU) arm during his shot at the rim.
Covington (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position with a bent forearm along Brown's (BOS) path during his drive.
Hayward (BOS) maintains a bent forearm to Westbrook's (HOU) back as he backs  him down in the post.
Harden (HOU) initiates contact with Theis (BOS) and extends his arm against his chest that subsequently creates contact with Tatum (BOS) affecting his driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) commits a take foul on Westbrook (HOU).
Hayward (BOS) commits a take foul on Westbrook (HOU).
Covington (HOU) and Tatum (BOS) engage and disengage off ball.
Westbrook (HOU) removes his arm from Smart's (BOS) side as he begins to move through his upward shooting motion.
Theis (BOS) commits a take foul on Westbrook (HOU).
Tucker (HOU) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
Green (HOU) and Smart (BOS) mutually engage during the loose ball.
Smart (BOS) cleanly dislodges the ball as he engages with Covington (HOU) during the rebound.
Harden (HOU) makes some contact to Hayward's (BOS) side during his drive however, the contact created is marginal.
Tucker (HOU) does not establish a legal position in Hayward's (BOS) path and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Westbrook (HOU) maintains legal position with a collapsed forearm to his side while contesting Smart's (BOS) driving shot attempt.
Theis (BOS) cleanly dislodges the ball before the ball makes contact with the backboard.
Tucker (HOU) jumps vertically along Tatum's (BOS) path while contesting his driving shot attempt.
Covington (HOU) places his hand to Theis' (BOS) side at the height of his trajectory during his shot near the rim however, the contact created is marginal.
Theis (BOS) and Covington (HOU) mutually engage during the rebound as both players move to the floor to retrieve the ball.
Harden (HOU) maintains a legal position with a bent forearm along Tatum's (BOS) path during his drive.
Tucker (HOU) engages with Smart (BOS) during the rebound, making hand on ball contact as Smart (BOS) secures the loose ball.
Harden (HOU) cleanly dislodges the ball following Smart's (BOS) gather.
Theis (BOS) makes contact with Harden's (HOU) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) places two hands to Tucker's (HOU) chest and slightly steers him into the screen before releasing.
Brown (BOS) slightly extends his off arm to Covington's (HOU) front as he releases from the contact to step back.
Westbrook (HOU) cleanly dislodges the ball as he engages with Theis' (BOS) during the rebound.
